"```sql\nSELECT constructors.url\nFROM constructorResults\nJOIN constructors ON constructorResults.constructorId = constructors.constructorId\nWHERE constructorResults.raceId = 9\nORDER BY constructorResults.points DESC\nLIMIT 1;\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the introduction website (URL) of the constructor that scored the highest points in the race with `raceId` 9. It joins the `constructorResults` table with the `constructors` table using the `constructorId` and orders the results by points in descending order, limiting the output to the top result."